    "name": "Golden Feather",
    "steam_appid": 3336150,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336150/extras/4c85bd91476be3744573cfa753339318.avif?t=1731661018\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336150/extras_big/4c85bd91476be3744573cfa753339318.avif?t=1731661018 width=800 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Golden Feather</strong> 是一款基于格林兄弟童话的短篇点击冒险游戏。这个童话将带给你一段难忘的旅程和愉快的故事。迷人的视觉效果和有趣的任务将让你保持娱乐。让自己放松，沉浸在这片充满氛围的童话世界中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336150/extras/28479a861fb04a9be13b2a5b0fe0ff59.avif?t=1731661018\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336150/extras_big/28479a861fb04a9be13b2a5b0fe0ff59.avif?t=1731661018 width=800 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>傻瓜能成为国王吗？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>这是一个关于小王子傻瓜的冒险故事。他接受国王的命令，踏上了寻找金鸟的旅程，但在途中他遇到了比金鸟更珍贵的东西。为了让童话故事有一个圆满的结局，愚人必须解开许多谜题，并表现出勇气，因为只有最优秀的人才能成为国王。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336150/extras/fc6c92fa2ef323db74fe7f1793bf5773.avif?t=1731661018\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336150/extras_big/fc6c92fa2ef323db74fe7f1793bf5773.avif?t=1731661018 width=800 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>安静与和平</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >厌倦了不断的压力和负面情绪吗？让自己放松一下！这个故事没有负面情绪和障碍，也没有善与恶的对立。它是一个适合晚上享受的童话故事，将为你带来平静，精美的视觉效果和愉快的音乐将帮助你沉浸在幻想世界的氛围中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336150/extras/1f83251c7d3b5b38814e8dc61722a748.avif?t=1731661018\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336150/extras_big/1f83251c7d3b5b38814e8dc61722a748.avif?t=1731661018 width=800 height=65 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好冒险了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个童话故事中，主人公都会有一个美好的结局，但这需要一些努力，所以准备好迎接挑战吧！在这个童话世界里，有许多有趣的事情在等着你！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多个场景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任务和谜题</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >秘密和收藏品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动听的背景音乐</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是我的第一款游戏，所以我没有机会进行高质量的本地化翻译。游戏使用了机器翻译，希望您能理解！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336150/extras/d1948aac57bd543443164cbb724b7b05.avif?t=1731661018\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336150/extras_big/d1948aac57bd543443164cbb724b7b05.avif?t=1731661018 width=800 height=59 /></span></p>",
